transcription.summary: The RingCentral integration with PC Recruiter only logs calls made on the primary phone number set in the PC Recruiter configuration. If a recruiter makes calls from a different number, those calls will not be logged in PC Recruiter unless they are also listed as a secondary phone number in the RingCentral Admin Center and all calls are synced to the same log.
